content: If you're having trouble taking on this supercharged enemy, a good thing to remember is that if it scrambles a bit to side to twirl about, it will either spew poison in a frontal arc, or go for a quick a pincer attack. Defeating this foe will earn you the Puppet Spider Spirit, and you can return back to the path outside.

The content is as follows:
If you're having trouble taking on this supercharged enemy, a good thing to remember is that if it scrambles a bit to side to twirl about, it will either spew poison in a frontal arc, or go for a quick a pincer attack. Defeating this foe will earn you the Puppet Spider Spirit, and you can return back to the path outside.
